50|$|In our Sun, {{only three}} types of modes have been found so far, namely p-, g- and f- modes. <b>Helioseismology</b> studies these modes with periods {{in the range of}} minutes, while for neutron stars the periods are much shorter, often seconds or even milliseconds.|$|E
